{"tid":2053390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《頭條新聞》被裁辱警風波 王喜慨嘆難捨香港之情","createTime":"2020-06-06T09:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T11:26:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1a72036195e13a45ca796fc519b37fd7fecd1151","tid":2053390,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z5Uo4irp4BY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZ5Uo4irp4BY&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=e7925b5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z5Uo4irp4BY</a><br />\n<br />\n【#抗爭時代】踏入六月，反送中運動將要踏入一周年。有人生活出現巨變，有人離開了，有人還在堅持。<br />\n<br />\n藝人王喜自從主持港台《頭條新聞》的《驚方訊息》環節，成為風眼中的風眼。近日節目被通訊局裁定辱警需要下架，他一臉無懼，轉向網上繼續發聲。<br />\n<br />\n一周年前夕，他接受訪問，談警察，談《頭條新聞》，也談年輕人等等話題。「每個人都有些難離難捨的東西&hellip;&hellip;我們看不到漁村變Hong Kong的過程，但是反過來，見證Hong Kong變『XIANG GANG』，都是一種福份來的。」王喜輕輕嘆息。<br />\n<br />\n說到最後，念茲在茲是香港這個家。"},{"pid":"3392945bc6d66519f9faaaf8c57cdb645a4ce306","tid":2053390,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:05:58.000Z","msg":"忠勇毅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772a188b206b074b394c81c50972b96c45c1b936","tid":2053390,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a82dac93fbcf55d8aa69e15ccd3608b8b9f50a","tid":2053390,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"當年我笑佢同陳志雲有基味，我做錯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.